            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et Genio huiusce <lb n="3"/>loci pro sal<lb break="no" n="4"/>ute dd<del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ominorum</ex></expan></del> nn<del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan></del> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Honoratus <lb n="6"/>|(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>reg</abbr><ex>ionarius</ex></expan> sub <lb n="7"/>cura <expan><abbr>Ful</abbr><ex>vi</ex></expan> Maximi co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Octob</abbr><ex>ribus</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Faustino et Rufino co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden als Spolie im Turm des spätantiken Binnenkastells von Környe. Z. 2: NI-, HVI-, CE-Ligaturen; Z. 4: TE-Ligatur; Z. 5: AT-Ligatur; S klein am Zeilenende im Winkel des V; Z. 7: DI-Ligatur; Z. 8: XI-, MI-Ligaturen; S klein am Zeilenende in O eingeschrieben; Z. 10: TI-, ET-, RV-, FI-Ligaturen. Blattförmige Hedera als Worttrenner in Z. 4. (B): Betz: kleinere LEseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
